# {{.ProjectName}}

## Project Overview

{{.Description}}

This is a Node.js/Express backend application using TypeScript.

## Tech Stack

- **Runtime**: Node.js 22 (LTS)
- **Framework**: Express.js
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 16
- **Testing**: Jest + Supertest
- **Linting**: ESLint + Prettier

## Commands

```bash
make dev          # Run development server
make start        # Start Docker Compose stack
make stop         # Stop Docker Compose stack
make test         # Run tests
make lint         # Run linter
make format       # Format code
make build        # Production build
```

## Project Structure

- `src/index.ts` - Server entry point
- `src/app.ts` - Express app configuration
- `src/routes/` - Route definitions
- `src/controllers/` - Request handlers with business logic
- `src/services/` - External service integrations
- `src/middleware/` - Express middleware (error handling, auth, etc.)
- `src/models/` - Data models and types
- `tests/` - Test files mirroring src structure
